Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.33,0:00:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真 雷 你们在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.33,0:00:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在模拟和Freedom的战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.63,0:00:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.30,0:00:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他很强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.72,0:00:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望大家现在能够了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止战火却不断蔓延的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.10,0:00:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 这场战争发生的真正原因
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.26,0:00:31.98,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,PLANT最高评议会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:28.98,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,诺伊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:30.73,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 克莉斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.69,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.11,0:00:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.53,0:00:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 关于这次播放我也完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 绝不能这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种整日互相伤害的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会有安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.21,0:00:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种无尽持续下去的仇恨连锁反应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们难道体验得还不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却有人无论如何都要阻碍这一切实现
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.59,0:00:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且是从很久以前开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,背后的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是热衷于制造敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.23,0:01:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热衷于为世界带来战争的军事产业复合体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.11,0:01:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死之商人 Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.86,0:01:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们才是我们这些期盼和平的人们真正的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.44,0:01:21.66,Default3,,0000,0000,0000,,奥布 内阁府官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:19.66,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:21.45,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 尤拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利塔 格鲁皮亚 克劳德氏他们的名字居然都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从心底盼望着不再发生战争的和平世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 告诉那些欲加以阻挠的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于世界真正的敌人Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣布一日不灭其根本誓不罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄兰达尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.44,0:01:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,展示出的人中有和赛兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是和奥布有着复杂关系的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.53,0:02:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不止是奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就没有任何国家和他们的全球化企业完全无关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狄兰达尔议长到底有什么打算
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 让大家困扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的想法正如刚才播放的内容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开战时防卫战之际所说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.52,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,容我在这里重复一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.64,0:02:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手中再次拿起的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.64,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次必须成为终结一切战斗之物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很担心奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今后赛兰打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.36,0:02:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也该从他们的战争系统中脱离出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们真正的敌人 不是联合也不是自然人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒Logos 只会一再重蹈覆辙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这谈何容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在既然看不到通往和平的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可选择的道路也就仅此而已了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则 这场战争永远不会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧 玛琉舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.65,0:03:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些不同于以往的东西正在蠢蠢欲动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赞成议长的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如他所说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次必须给这战争的历史划上休止符
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.29,0:03:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向您的决断与勇气致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-wax 006来电
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,区域3 地点1.36有不明物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有行动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报告司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另外重写资料库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那已经不是不明 而是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队司令部来电
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva前往支援即将进行的Angel Down作战
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10 绕进地面的阴影处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valient 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玛琉舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好 被他们压制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.61,0:06:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是ZAFT为何突然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来完全被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右舷后方又出现BuCUE 8
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10点方向也再出现BABI 9
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.63,0:07:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回避
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.88,0:07:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.84,0:07:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解尽量避免无意义的战斗是这艘船的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这样下去会被击沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.97,0:07:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请下达直击的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您不承认 至少让我们的Murasame队…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 但是基拉也说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许让我们攻击正是对方的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿玛基上尉 让我们出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murasame一台也不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全数带回奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要想办法出海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前大家要坚持住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标 再向西10
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.60,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁队BABI 全队中弹 返航
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是传说中的Freedom和Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.69,0:08:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫M.S.队别太急躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则支持不到Minerva赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因为温吞地驱赶才使我方渐渐不利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.03,0:08:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没等到Minerva 只要出动全军
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吧 阿拉斯加和雅金·多维战役
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欲速则不达
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为长远着想 还是让Minerva和Impulse来了断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按命令交给我军的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,议长是说要打倒Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.77,0:08:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那为何要去攻击Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这道命令绝对有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请再一次向司令部…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经确认过了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.15,0:08:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是答覆不变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不表明目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一味扰乱战场扩大战火的Archangel和Freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到今后局势 必须铲除这个潜在的威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是本国的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经无能为力了 作战早已开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到A-wax传来的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,显示情况图
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也别再止足不前了 阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白你不想跟以前的战友作战
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 时过境迁 人心也会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是也变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着现在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 已收到A-wax的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达作战区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想看的话就待在房间里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 和那艘船作战我们也会以死相拼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰桥遮蔽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发令红色状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.48,0:10:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对舰对M.S.战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发令红色状态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员请在搭乘机内待命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,CIWS Tristan Isolde启动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射管一号至三号 全炮门装填Parsifal
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 你做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:23.60,Default2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.82,0:11:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿斯兰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.45,0:11:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离地点20 即将遇敌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射干扰弹 Impulse出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.33,0:11:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探测器…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是干扰弹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舵10 下降
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真·飞鸟 核心战机出击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捕捉到Archangel 距离2000
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isolde 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 为什么那艘船要…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连那都能避开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让库拉提斯露两手给我们看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 别胡乱移动就不会中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然没打算击中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳 打开国际救援频道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.89,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是ZAFT舰Minerva舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔利雅·库拉提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Archangel 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 Minerva发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰奉司令部命令前来击沉贵舰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果贵舰现在停止包括舰载机在内的一切攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投降的话 本舰也会停止攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.47,0:14:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命令可是击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库拉提斯这家伙到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此一次警告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.06,0:14:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过时不候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:15:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向你们保证乘员的生命安全
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,望贵舰三思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是那艘Minerva的舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想与之为敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果在这里向ZAFT投降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.00,0:15:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡嘉莉大人的安全…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿玛基
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去海上 送卡嘉莉回奥布
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以此为最优先
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米莉雅丽亚 打开和对方相同的频道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.81,0:15:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.02,0:15:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Archangel舰长 玛琉·拉米亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感谢贵舰的好意 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.62,0:15:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰还有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.67,0:16:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,联合还是PLANT
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界正被分为两种颜色时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本舰似乎又成了碍眼的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.13,0:16:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但正因为如此 更不能在这里被抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.76,0:16:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿能允许我们脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.39,0:16:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,库拉提斯这蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.23,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看你干了什么蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让M.S.队重新开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被小看了 绝不允许他们逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.42,0:16:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维拉德队长 怎么自作主张
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不攻击就会让他们逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们自己不也这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.43,0:17:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是FAITH
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.52,0:17:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此胆小的妇人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被人羞辱怎能就此罢休
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.98,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minerva不干的话由我们来干
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总是这一招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.54,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为一直能奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真 别…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freedom的确动作迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击也准确
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那台机体绝对不瞄准驾驶舱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.29,0:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻击的总是武装和主监视器
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impulse的胜机就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳 胸部组件 Force Silhouette
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你杀了史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都那么拼命想阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离海岸线10
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样支撑不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请出动Murasame
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甩掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这里总是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.05,0:19:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天得在这里被我打下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,梅琳 Sword Silhouette
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即将到达海岸线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会被逃脱的 舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tannhauser 启动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标 Archangel
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.34,0:20:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急隔离壁封闭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备下潜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.55,0:20:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉 基拉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉大人的话不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.39,0:20:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放出Rouge
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快 让它下潜就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样总算…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾相信的是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.04,0:23:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是认为不会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.75,0:23:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像万花筒般变换意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是世界 还是自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.34,0:23:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为战士们准备的下一个舞台是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.43,0:23:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 机动战士Gundam Seed Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混沌的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.18,0:23:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,降落到梦想的世界吧 Destiny
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-------------OPJP-------------
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:25.92,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕たちは迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.92,0:04:30.95,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,たどり着く場所を探しつづけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.95,0:04:35.34,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,悲しくて涙流しても
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.34,0:04:40.26,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつか輝きにかえて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:51.70,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,閉ざした過去が今
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.98,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,胸を搖さぶるから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.37,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,求めるほど遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.80,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りの心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:03.44,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕らは生きるほど何かを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:05.94,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,それでも明日への
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.15,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,夢を捨てたくない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:12.84,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみの理由でさえも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:17.34,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,つよく抱きしめていたい
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:22.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,通りすぎた季節のその先に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:27.31,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,なにがあるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.73,0:05:34.06,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,僕たちは迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:39.04,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,たどり着く場所を探しつづけ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:43.47,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,悲しくて涙流しても
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:48.38,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,いつか輝きにかえて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.38,0:05:51.20,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,Cause I'm never gonna stop streak in my dream!
